rComments: A very interesting professor, but his final exam was a bit difficult even though I studied quite a bit.

Mr. Fennell seems like a very nice guy. I would sometimes have trouble paying attention (class was a bit early for me,) but when I did it was usually interesting. He posts lecture slides online. Tests come from those.

I thought this class would be boring, but he finds a way to make archaeology interesting. The book is useful, but skimming it is fine if you will read it at all. He's a good speaker and loves talking about the New Philadelphia site. I highly recommend this professor.
